OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,6,Fsome heavy, with some coastal haar
OL,7,Fpossible. Tending to brighten up over
OL,8,FAberdeenshire but as temperatures pick
OL,9,Fup this could set off some thundery
OL,10,Fshowers. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with showery
OL,13,Frain, some heavy at first. Overnight
OL,14,Fbecoming drier with more scattered
OL,15,Fshowers, and the odd clear interval.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FSome bright or sunny
OL,18,Fintervals but also a few showers,
OL,19,Fwhich could turn heavy and thundery
OL,20,Fover Moray in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
